title: Merge pull request #4 from ccamara/translation-catalan
message:
Merge pull request #4 from ccamara/translation-catalan

Thanks again to Javier and Carlos for your translations! The extra styles.xml files for particular languages are there on purpose and should not be removed. We have done our best to make the layouts as liquid as possible and independent on the language, but it is not always possible. They are basically there to correct layout issues that arise when long words or similar break the layout.
